{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"791a53b8b8","title":"在中央政治局武昌扩大会议上的讲话提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"30a6e91e56","index":0,"year":1958,"month":11,"day":21,"articleId":"791a53b8b8"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d8ad156cb3","type":"title","text":"在中央政治局武昌扩大会议上的讲话提纲","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"790f17bbe0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）过渡到共产主义问题","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"e86b767e6c","type":"paragraph","text":"中国和苏联哪个先过渡到共产主义？要从各方面慎重考虑。中国早过渡究竟有无可能，是否有利。即使有可能，也可以用社会主义之名，行共产主义之实。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"0ad2645190","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）十五年规划问题。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"f3dd704fc6","type":"paragraph","text":"四十条放两年再说，不可外传，勿务虚名而获实锅。长期计划可以不必作，只要少数人中间有一种考虑。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"4b793dfd72","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）全会任务问题。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"496c2793da","type":"paragraph","text":"就搞人民公社指示和明年指标。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"e08653018a","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）社会主义和共产主义之间要不要划线，如何划法，是否提三四年、五六年过渡到全民所有制。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"a798624925","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）消火阶级问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"9c6254a3ac","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联的提法和我们的提法。经济上消灭阶级不等于政治上思想上消灭阶级。苏联的教训和中国的教训。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"215043f052","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）商品经济问题","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"f76b5bd579","type":"paragraph","text":"商品的范围。商品的寿命。斯大林的提法和政治经济学教科书第三版的提法","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"cb41bb9704","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）减少任务问题","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"9ba35cb6ca","type":"paragraph","text":"工业任务、水利任务、粮食任务都要适当收缩。是否泼冷水是否机会主义？一定要有客观可能性。过了明年六月再看","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"560a4cd28a","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）人民公社整社问题","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"},{"id":"affe985e59","type":"paragraph","text":"用四个月整社。公社、食堂、托儿所，跨不跨的两种可能性","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8"}],"page":{"id":"597ed6968e","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"791a53b8b8","start":460,"end":461}}}},"__N_SSG":true}